objects.name: auth_group
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE "auth_group" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "name" varchar(150) NOT NULL UNIQUE)

objects.name: auth_group_permissions
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE "auth_group_permissions" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "group_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "auth_group" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "permission_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "auth_permission" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)

objects.name: auth_permission
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE "auth_permission" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "content_type_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "django_content_type" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "codename" varchar(100) NOT NULL, "name" varchar(255) NOT NULL)

objects.name: django_admin_log
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE "django_admin_log" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "object_id" text NULL, "object_repr" varchar(200) NOT NULL, "action_flag" smallint unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("action_flag" >= 0), "change_message" text NOT NULL, "content_type_id" integer NULL REFERENCES "django_content_type" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "user_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "nail_service_user" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "action_time" datetime NOT NULL)

objects.name: django_content_type
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE "django_content_type" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "app_label" varchar(100) NOT NULL, "model" varchar(100) NOT NULL)

objects.name: django_migrations
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE "django_migrations" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "app" varchar(255) NOT NULL, "name" varchar(255) NOT NULL, "applied" datetime NOT NULL)

objects.name: django_session
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE "django_session" ("session_key" varchar(40) NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY, "session_data" text NOT NULL, "expire_date" datetime NOT NULL)

objects.name: nail_service_customer
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE "nail_service_customer" ("user_id" bigint NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY REFERENCES "nail_service_user" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)

objects.name: nail_service_customer_masters
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE "nail_service_customer_masters" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "customer_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "nail_service_customer" ("user_id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "master_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "nail_service_master" ("user_id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)

objects.name: nail_service_customer_services
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE "nail_service_customer_services" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "customer_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "nail_service_customer" ("user_id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "services_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "nail_service_services" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)

objects.name: nail_service_events
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE "nail_service_events" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "title" varchar(255) NOT NULL, "start_date" datetime NOT NULL, "end_date" datetime NOT NULL, "master_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "nail_service_master" ("user_id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)

objects.name: nail_service_master
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE "nail_service_master" ("user_id" bigint NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY REFERENCES "nail_service_user" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)

objects.name: nail_service_master_customers
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE "nail_service_master_customers" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "master_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "nail_service_master" ("user_id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "customer_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "nail_service_customer" ("user_id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)

objects.name: nail_service_pricelist
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE "nail_service_pricelist" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "price" decimal NOT NULL, "time_service" time NULL, "service_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "nail_service_services" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "master_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "nail_service_master" ("user_id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)

objects.name: nail_service_services
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE "nail_service_services" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "name" varchar(255) NOT NULL UNIQUE, "price" decimal NOT NULL, "time_service" time NOT NULL)

objects.name: nail_service_user
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE "nail_service_user" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "password" varchar(128) NOT NULL, "last_login" datetime NULL, "is_superuser" bool NOT NULL, "username" varchar(150) NOT NULL UNIQUE, "first_name" varchar(150) NOT NULL, "last_name" varchar(150) NOT NULL, "email" varchar(254) NOT NULL, "is_staff" bool NOT NULL, "is_active" bool NOT NULL, "date_joined" datetime NOT NULL, "role" varchar(50) NOT NULL)

objects.name: nail_service_user_groups
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE "nail_service_user_groups" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "user_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "nail_service_user" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "group_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "auth_group" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)

objects.name: nail_service_user_user_permissions
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE "nail_service_user_user_permissions" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "user_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "nail_service_user" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "permission_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "auth_permission" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)
